out him from other business owners and various speaking events many years ago. After meeting him in LA years ago, we hit it off as friends and recently I hired him to sell my social media company. I couldnt be more happy with the results! If you want an honest, ethical team of M&amp;A advisors who truly care about you and your company, go with Vinehurst.'),(12226,1876,'_author','John Davidson'),(12227,1876,'featured','-1'),(12228,1876,'_featured_plan','-1'),(12229,1876,'_drop_shadow','-1'),(12230,1876,'_column_bigger','-1'),(12231,1876,'_share_button','-1'),(12232,1875,'textfalse',''),(12233,1875,'_desc','When I contacted Vinehurst I knew by viewing their website that they mainly work with mid-sized companies. However, being a very small business of less then $50k a year in profits, I wanted to pick their brain on how I could grow my business. Chris answered the phone and talked with me for an hour, giving me great advice that I have put to good use. Thank you Chris for taking the time to help me, I will be coming to you when Im ready to sell in a few years!'),(12234,1875,'_author','Samantha Heines'),(12235,1875,'featured','-1'),(12236,1875,'_featured_plan','-1'),(12237,1875,'_drop_shadow','-1'),(12238,1875,'_column_bigger','-1'),(12239,1875,'_share_button','-1'),(12240,1875,'_company','Small Business Owner'),(12241,1876,'_company','Website Business Owner'),(12218,1875,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(12219,1875,'_edit_lock','1468084972:2'),(12220,1875,'_edit_last','2'),(12221,1876,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(12222,1876,'_edit_lock','1467130884:1'),(12223,1876,'_edit_last','1'),(12224,1876,'textfalse',''),(15243,2380,'header_color_gradient_angle','vertical'),(15244,2380,'header_size','false'),(15245,2380,'header_source','no-image'),(15798,2425,'textfalse',''),(15799,2425,'_layout','default'),(12405,1913,'_thumbnail_id','1918'),(12406,1913,'_template','no-title'),(12407,1913,'_wpb_vc_js_status','true'),(12408,1913,